data.description: NOW OFFERING $10,000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS, RATE BUY DOWN or to REPLACE CARPET. Additionally, a 2-10 HOME WARRANTY will be provided to buyers! Like NEW construction, without the wait! Come see this 2020 home built by Lennar in the thriving community of Connerton Village. The Winthrop has 5 bedrooms and 3 and a half bathrooms. The kitchen features clean, shaker cabinets and stainless steel appliances. The master suite is located on the first floor with a walk-in closet that connects to the laundry room for maximum convenience. Luxurious crown molding can be appreciated throughout the first floor. Upstairs, there are 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a large, versatile loft. The loft can be used as a home office, homework station or game room – the possibilities are endless. This home is outfitted with three walk-in closets and plenty of pantries for all of your storage needs. This home is conveniently located in Connerton, a desirable, master planned community in the heart of Land O’ Lakes. This community offers every amenity you could ever dream of! Relax by the resort-like, maintenance-free community pool. Pick up a new hobby such as pickleball or tennis. Playgrounds and parks are also available for residents to enjoy. Or, jump on your golf cart to play a round at The Groves Golf and Country Club. Upon completion of this community, there will be 5,000 homes featuring a town center and countless amenities. There are hospitals, assisted living, shopping, dining and so much more nearby. With proximity to major highways and transportation options, commuting to work or exploring the greater Tampa Bay area is a breeze. It’s time to see this beautiful home for yourself!
